		{
			dependencies: ["33AE8B292B528D0C"]
			description: [
				"&5Dense Hydrazine&r technically involves slowly chewing through &7palladium&r, so it's perhaps not the most viable fuel source, but it's required to build the Tier 2 rocket parts."
				""
				"You will need &dstable titanium machine casings&r on your &2chemplant&r to produce it."
