		}
		{
			description: [
				"It might seem anachronistic, but the next tier of &drocket fuel&r requires several chemicals that must be extracted from &ecoal or charcoal processing&r."
				""
				"&6Ethylbenzene&r is distilled from &acoal gas&r, which can be extracted from carbon fuels by processing them with steam in a &2Pyrolyse Oven&r. If you use a &bDistillation Tower&r, this will also yield &acoal tar&r."
				""
				"&6Naphthalene&r, &6Anthracene&r, &6Phenol&r, and &6Durene&r are distilled from &acoal tar&r. The &6Anthracene&r yield is pretty low, but you won't need much &drocket fuel&r unless you plan on using it for power."
			]
