		{
			description: [
				"Spectroscopy readings indicate a high concentration of &6Tungsten&r on &eVenus&r and &cMars&r, a dense metal that can form the basis for many new and valuable alloys."
				""
				"Traveling to &3The Moon&r took Apollo 3 days, but &eVenera-9&r took 4 months to get to &eVenus&r and &cViking&r took &o&e11 months&r to get to &cMars&r. "
				""
				"The &9basic rocket motor&r and &9fuel tanks&r don't seem up to the task for such an operation.  New technology is required."
				""
				"Thankfully, it seems like &6Titanium&r is sturdy enough to form the base of a more powerful engine and a tank capable of storing gaseous fuels at higher pressures."
